            <a href="/">Home</a>
<a href="/menu" class="active">Menu</a>
<a href="/catering">Catering</a>
<a href={giftCardLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gift Cards</a>
          </div>

          <button class="mobile-menu-icon" id="menuToggle" aria-label="Open menu" aria-expanded="false" type="button">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <header class="hero">
        <i class="sprinkle sprinkle-1"></i>
        <i class="sprinkle sprinkle-2"></i>
        <i class="sprinkle sprinkle-3"></i>
        <i class="sprinkle sprinkle-4"></i>

        <h1>Current Flavors</h1>

        <p class="hero-copy">
          Our rotating monthly menu features artisanal ice cream, seasonal scoops,
          and dairy-free options handcrafted in Cody, Wyoming.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-kicker">
          Rotating Monthly &nbsp; • &nbsp; Small-Batch &nbsp; • &nbsp; Made in Cody
        </div>
      </header>

      <main>
        <section class="container" aria-label="Menu highlights">
          <div class="feature-pills">
            <div class="feature-pill"><strong>↻</strong> Rotating Monthly</div>
            <div class="feature-pill"><strong>🍦</strong> Small-Batch</div>
            <div class="feature-pill"><strong>🌿</strong> Dairy-Free Options</div>
            <div class="feature-pill"><strong>📍</strong> Made in Cody</div>
          </div>

          
<section class="collection-section" aria-label="Flavor collections">
  <div class="collection-heading">
    <span>Explore Our</span>
    <h2>Flavor Collections</h2>
    <p>Four delicious ways to find your perfect scoop.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="collection-grid">
    <article class="collection-card collection-classics">
      <div class="collection-art" aria-hidden="true">🍦</div>

      <div class="collection-copy">
        <h3>The Classics</h3>
        <p>
          Our Classic Series pays homage to the timeless favorites that have stood
          the test of time and continue to delight ice cream enthusiasts. Join us
          for a scoop or two! and experience the joy of our Classic Series.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="collection-card collection-limited">
      <div class="collection-art" aria-hidden="true">🏅</div>

      <div class="collection-copy">
        <h3>Limited Edition</h3>
        <p>
          Discover new and exciting flavors with our Limited Edition Series! Our
          expert ice cream makers are constantly pushing the boundaries to create
          flavors that are truly one-of-a-kind. Each month, we unveil a new lineup
          of flavors that are available for a limited time only.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="collection-card collection-dairy">
      <div class="collection-art" aria-hidden="true">🥥</div>

      <div class="collection-copy">
        <h3>Dairy-Free Decadence</h3>
        <p>
          Our Dairy-free Decadence series is made with a coconut milk ice cream
          base, creating a deliciously creamy and rich texture. Each scoop is
          filled with bold and indulgent flavors that will leave you feeling
          satisfied and happy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="collection-card collection-boozy">
      <div class="collection-art" aria-hidden="true">🍸</div>

      <div class="collection-copy">
        <h3>Boozy Delight</h3>
        <p>
          Experience a new level of indulgence with our Boozy Delight Series!
          We've blended our creamy, delicious ice cream with a splash of your
          favorite spirits for a decadent treat that's sure to please.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="filters" aria-label="Flavor filters">
